  	  We want to end dependence on Excel.
  	</p>
    <p><i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin fa-3x"></i></p>
    <p class="lead">
  	  For a reseller with thousands of orders, keeping data on Excel can cause many problems:
  	</p>
    <p class="lead">
  	  <em>Sales productivity decreases as the number of records and users increase.</em>
  	</p>
  	<p class="lead">
  	  <em>Too many worksheets make it hard to visualize how data fits together.</em>
  	</p>
  	<p class="lead">
  	  <em>A hardware failure or virus can potentialy mess up the data files.</em>
  	</p>
