  	<p class="lead home-text text-muted">
  	  Gotato was built to solve those problems.
  	</p>
  	<p class="lead home-text">How?</p>
  </div>
</div>

<legend></legend>
<div class="row" style="padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px;">
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 col-md-offset-2">
	<h2>Smart and Simple</h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    Gotato automatically does all the heavy lifting for our users, from calculate data to generate sale reports. Gotato minimizes the hassle our users have to face daily in Excel.
  </p>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    Users can view all information on the same page with spreadsheet-style interface.
  </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
    <%= image_tag("placeit.png.jpg", :alt => "graph", class: "image") %>
  </div>
</div>


