<div class="row" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 30px;">
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
    <%= image_tag("placeit.png", :alt => "graph", class: "image2") %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5">
  <h2>Accessible</h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    Work as a team. Our user, with a manager account, at the U.S. can work on the same data with a seller in VN seamlessly. All users can access the database anytime, anywhere.
